from combinatorial.zoo import  G2_SQUARE_BOUNDED, G2_SQUARE_UNBOUNDED

from combinatorial.gmaps import nGmap

B = nGmap.from_string(G2_SQUARE_BOUNDED)
U = nGmap.from_string(G2_SQUARE_UNBOUNDED)

list (B.all_i_cells(0))

list (B.all_i_cells(1))

list (B.all_i_cells(2))

B.D.print_alpha_table()

for e, edge in enumerate (B.D.all_i_cells (1)):
    for v, vertex in enumerate (B.D.all_i_cells (0)):
        e_darts = list (edge)
        v_darts = list (vertex)
        i = B.D.incident(1,e_darts[0], 0, v_darts[0])
        print (f'e{e} incident with v{v}: {i}')
